 ethnic name for someone from Flanders, Middle Dutch <i>vleminc</i>."]},{"name":"Flanders","meanings":["English: ethnic name from Middle English <i>Fla(u)ndres</i> ‘Flanders’, denoting someone from Flanders, a historical region covering parts of modern-day Belgium, France, and the Netherlands. Compare   Fleming  ."]},{"name":"Fleeman","meanings":["English: variant of   Fleming  ."]},{"name":"Flemming","meanings":["German: ethnic name for someone from Flanders, Middle High German <i>vlaeminc</i>. People from Flanders spread throughout Germany, as well as England, in the Middle Ages as clothmakers and dyers.","English: variant of   Fleming  ."]},{"name":"Flamenco","meanings":["Spanish: ethnic name from <i>flamenco</i> ‘Fleming, Flemish person’ (see   Fleming  )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Fleming was born in 1218, in Westmorland, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 daughter with Fleming."},"et":{"1218–":"1218–Surnud","1218–Male":"1218–Surnud","1238–Female":"1238–Surnud","1218–Female":"1218–Surnud","1238":"1238","Bef 1238":"enne 1238","1218":"1218","Westmorland, England, United Kingdom":"Westmorland, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Cumberland, England":"Cumberland, England"},"fi":{"1218–":"1218–Kuollut","1218–Male":"1218–Kuollut","1238–Female":"1238–Kuollut","1218–Female":"1218–Kuollut","1238":"1238","Bef 1238":"ennen vuotta 1238","1218":"1218","Westmorland, England, United Kingdom":"Westmorland, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Cumberland, England":"Cumberland, England"},"fr":{"1218–":"1218–Décédée","1218–Male":"1218–Décédé","1238–Female":"1238–Décédée","1218–Female":"1218–Décédée","1238":"1238","Bef 1238":"avant 1238","1218":"1218","Westmorland, England, United Kingdom":"Westmorland, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Cumberland, England":"Cumberland, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Fleming est née en 1218, à Westmorland, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec Fleming."},"de":{"1218–":"1218–Verstorben","1218–Male":"1218–Verstorben","1238–Female":"1238–Verstorbe